(88, 'Live-Action : Machida-kun\'s world (Machida-kun no Sekai)', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;&quot;&gt;Satu lagi rekomendasi film untuk tahun 2019, Machida-kun\'s world sebuat film adaptasi dari manga Machida-kun\'s world (Machida-kun no &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;&quot;&gt;Sekai) karya Yuki Ando.&lt;img style=&quot;float: right;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdnx.natalie.mu/media/news/comic/2019/0505/machida_pos_fixw_234.jpg&quot; /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;&quot;&gt;Manga yang dirilis dari tahun 2013 sampai tahun 2018 ini telah banyak memenangkan penghargaan seperti p&lt;span lang=&quot;id&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot;&gt;ada 2015, Machida-kun&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;id&quot; style=&quot;font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot;&gt;no Sekai memenangkan Penghargaan Wajah Baru Festival Media Jepang ke-19; dan pada tahun 2016, dianugerahi Penghargaan Pencipta Baru Tezuka Osamu ke-20.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;id&quot; style=&quot;font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Sinopsis:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p id=&quot;tw-target-text&quot; class=&quot;tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot; data-placeholder=&quot;Translation&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;id&quot; style=&quot;font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot;&gt; Machida, yang menghadapi semua orang dengan lurus, sosok karakter yang emosinya digerakkan orang-orang sekitar, dan saat ketika Machida menemukan &quot;perasaan yang tidak mengerti&quot; pertama ditampilkan.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot; data-placeholder=&quot;Translation&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;id&quot; style=&quot;font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Trailler&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot; data-placeholder=&quot;Translation&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;id&quot; style=&quot;font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;iframe src=&quot;//www.youtube.com/embed/6uX2Zz8IvqM&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;337&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;allowfullscreen&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;&quot;&gt;Film &quot;Machida-kun\'s world&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;&quot;&gt;Dirilis pada hari Jumat, 7 Juni 2019&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;&quot;&gt;Asli: Yuki Ando &quot;Machida-kun no Sekai&quot; (diterbitkan Komik Shueisha Margaret)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;&quot;&gt;Direktur: Yuya Ishii&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;&quot;&gt;Skenario: Sho Kataoka, Yuya Ishii&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;&quot;&gt;Musik: Kono Takeyo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;&quot;&gt;perencanaan dan produksi: North Island Naoaki&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;&quot;&gt;Pemain: Hosoda KeiHisashiFutoshi, Sekimizunagisa, Iwata Takanori, Takahata Mitsuki, Maeda Atsuko, Taiga, Ikematsu Sogo, Toda Erika, Sato Koichi, Kitamura Aikusu, Matsushima Nanako&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;&quot;