Yashiro (Domestik na Kanojo)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Ryuuhei Nabeshima: Chado Horii (Ballroom e Youkoso)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Masahiro Saki: KENN (Kyoukai no Kanata)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Madoka Yabuchi: Sayaka Senbongi (Animegataris)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Nao Nanao: Yuna Taniguchi (Parade Kematian)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Yuka Kurumatani: Aya Endou (Shirokuma Cafe)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Staf&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Desain Prop: Hideki Fukushima (desain mekanis Zegapain ADP), Michiko Makita (Action Heroine Cheer Fruits)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Direktur Seni: Maho Takahashi (Gerbang: Jieitai Kanochi nite, Kaku Tatakaeri)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Desain Warna: Miyuki Sunako (Boku no Kanojo ga Majimesugiru Sho-jalang na Ken)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Direktur Fotografi: Youko Ootake (Fotografi Chio-chan no Tsuugakuro)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Pengeditan: Toshihiko Kojima (Mayoiga)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Sutradara Suara: Jin Aketagawa (Yagate Kimi ni Naru)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;OP&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Musik: Hiroaki Tsutsumi (Rokudenashi Majutsu Koushi ke Akashic Records) Band rock alternatif Jepang akan membawakan lagu tema pembuka &quot;Happy Go Ducky!&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;